com.ibm.team.build.client.iterator
Interface IBuildResultRecordIterator

public interface IBuildResultRecordIterator

Provides the ability to iterate through the build result records associated with a set of build results.

          The maximum number of build result records that can be retrieved in one invocation of IBuildResultRecordIterator.next(int, IProgressMonitor).

Returns the next numRecords of build result records and positions the iterator at the next record beyond them. Less than the desired number of records may be returned if there are not enough records left to fulfill the request.

Parameters:

progressMonitor - The progress monitor to track progress on or null if progress monitoring is not desired.
